('1412191817475171453', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ypdRDq5Y2soAgrxgQKOvy7rw6b3oQGs0aGnGGficGvn5Gj1cgfusw4JNDCibSykrgQKj2ibPiaRjCcARhwb4jCg27A/0?tp=webp" /></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	<span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">舌战群儒展雄风，针锋相对辩天下。精英荟萃显才华，英雄齐聚论时事。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	<span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">法律是哲学的入世，政治的产物，力量的博弈，历史的沉淀，道德的强制，利益的调和。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	<span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">律师有着敏锐的洞察能力，严谨的思维方式，深厚的理论功底。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	<span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">当法律遇上律师，法律的价值将会彰显无遗；当律师遇上律师，法律的功效将发挥极致。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	<span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">如何辨别黑白？如何分清善恶？如何辨别真假？</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	<span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">协力，将带您走进律师职业的神秘殿堂！</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 25px; line-height: 25px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important;">\r\n	<strong style="max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !im